      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the F22C1 inline-four, featuring a forged crankshaft and fiber-reinforced metal cylinder liners, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency through its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a crisp, short-throw 6-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis maintains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension geometry, offering telepathic steering feedback and a perfect 50/50 weight distribution. This example is in immaculate, showroom condition with zero mechanical lash, pristine underbody components, and sharp VTEC engagement. A truly unmolested specimen for the serious driving purist.",
